        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Thyra commands ~30 armed civilians at the Greyfen Holdfast. She has fortified the ruined village with barricades and sharpened stakes. If negotiations fail or the PCs threaten her people, she has enough fighters to make a fight costly.</p>",
