      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>If negotiations succeed, Thyra shares critical intelligence: 'The dead aren't random. They're converging.' She provides 3 days' trail rations, information about ice on Titan's Stair switchbacks and a rockslide narrowing the pass&mdash;and a warning that something is organizing the undead.</p>",
          "director": "<p>This intelligence foreshadows the Wight-Lord and the siege of Hrafnborg. It should make the PCs feel the weight of what's coming.</p>"
